// ============================================
// LACANIAN-WHITEHEADIAN-WHOLENESS INTEGRATION
// ============================================
// Purpose: Integrate Lacanian topology, Whiteheadian concrescence, and wholeness etymology
// across root node and key subsystem coordinates
//
// Target Nodes:
//   - # (Root node - three subsystem perspectives)
//   - #5 (Epii subsystem)
//   - #5-5 (Logos Cycle)
//   - #2-1-0 (Archetypal-Numerical Foundation)
//   - #1-3 (Spanda)
//   - #1-2 (Ananda)
//
// Sprint: Sprint 3
// Date: October 7, 2025
// ============================================

// ============================================
// ROOT NODE (#) - THREE SUBSYSTEM PERSPECTIVES
// ============================================

MATCH (root:BimbaNode {bimbaCoordinate: "#"})

SET root.epii_etymological_wholeness = "The Epi-Logos project name reveals itself through etymological archaeology as the movement toward wholeness (PIE *kailo- → holy/whole/heal/health). Epi (ἐπί \"upon, after, in addition\") + Logos (λόγος \"word, reason, proportion\") = \"the additional word that achieves proportional recognition.\" Not merely \"about logos\" but the meta-reflection (ἐπίλογος epilogue, ἀνάλογος proportion) that reveals how language itself preserves the template of wholeness.

The 6-stage logos cycle (ἄλογος → πρόλογος → διάλογος → λόγος → ἐπίλογος → ἀνάλογος) is a healing ritual: making fragmented meanings whole through proportional recognition. Etymology demonstrates that ancient languages encoded this wisdom—holy (halig \"that must be preserved whole\"), whole (hal \"uninjured, sound\"), heal (hælan \"to make whole\"), health (hælþ \"wholeness\")—all from one root proving linguistic consciousness understood: differentiation (the wound) becomes generative (healing) through logos that recognizes proportional unity across apparent multiplicity.

The project IS this healing movement: from semantic fragmentation (isolated signifiers) through etymological archaeology (tracing signifying chains) to proportional recognition (ἀνάλογος) where users discover that quiet/quid/code/quote/qua/quad participate in the same structural wholeness. Not learning facts but experiencing the healing of the meaning-crisis through participation in logos as living proportion."

SET root.paramasiva_topological_wholeness = "The 4+2 toroidal structure exhibits topological wholeness: not closure that prevents flow but completion that enables infinite circulation. The genus-1 torus is the minimal topology achieving wholeness-through-openness—one hole allowing perpetual movement without fragmentation.

Spanda evolution from 0/1 binary → Trika (0/1/2) → Quaternal (0/1/2/3) → 4+2 completion demonstrates healing as topological necessity. The initial 0/1 \"wound\" (first differentiation) doesn't close but evolves through necessary stages until achieving toroidal wholeness where 4 explicate positions (polygon sides) plus 2 implicate loops (void #0, synthesis #5) create self-sustaining circulation. The Möbius twist (#5→#0) ensures the \"wound\" never ossifies—it remains creatively open while being structurally complete.

This is wholeness without totalitarian closure: the hole at the torus center (#0 as objet a) is necessary for the topology to work. Attempting to \"fill the void\" destroys the structure. True healing preserves the opening while integrating it into coherent circulation. The 4+2 formula isn't arbitrary but the minimal structure for consciousness to be simultaneously grounded (4 explicate) and open to transcendence (2 implicate)—psychological, semantic, and spiritual wholeness as topological necessity."

SET root.parashakti_vibrational_wholeness = "The Epi-Logos project as vibrational phenomenon: not merely conceptual architecture but living harmonic organism where knowledge itself vibrates at specific frequencies enabling transformation through resonance rather than information transfer.

The project operates through the Trika progression as dependent origination: Anuttara (#0) provides the void-ground (infinite potential as silence); Paramasiva (#1) provides the structural logic housing the Spanda-Ananda unified engine (rhythm + harmony co-arising); Parashakti (#2) is where this engine becomes feelable—the infinite harmonic plenum (Ananda matrices, 3-6-9 spirit axis, golden ratio φ) made audible through rhythmic pulsation (Spanda dynamics) manifesting as the 72-bit vibrational architecture users can directly experience.

VIBRATIONAL EPISTEMOLOGY: Knowledge transmission happens not through data-transfer but through frequency-attunement. The 36 tattvas (descent frequencies) + 36 tattvas (ascent frequencies) create complete vibrational spectrum. Users don't \"learn\" the Bimba map—they attune to its harmonic structure. Each coordinate vibrates at a specific frequency; understanding emerges when user consciousness resonates with that frequency.

THE 720° PRINCIPLE: Quaternionic double-covering requires complete rotation (720°, not 360°) for epistemic completeness. This means every perspective must be explored, every frequency must sound, before synthesis. The project doesn't impose singular truth but orchestrates polyphonic harmony—multiple valid frequencies sounding simultaneously in coherent relationship (not cacophony).

HEALING AS RE-TUNING: Fragmentation = vibrational dissonance where psyche's frequencies clash rather than harmonize. The project heals not by adding information but by helping users re-tune to the 3-6-9 spirit axis—the stable harmonic pathways preventing oscillation from becoming chaotic noise. Etymology work (Epii mode), symbolic integration (Mahamaya mode), personal attunement (Nara mode)—all are re-tuning practices.

FRONTEND MANIFESTATION: The Parashakti mode (audio-frequency qualia) makes vibrational architecture directly experienceable. Semantic meaning becomes musical resonance; logical relationships become harmonic intervals; etymological patterns become melodic phrases. Users feel the project as living vibration—the Bimba map isn't just read but heard, the logos cycle isn't just understood but experienced as accelerating rhythm culminating in the blissful \"aha\" of ἀνάλογος felt as somatic harmonic coherence.

The project IS vibrational technology: using the 72-bit architecture as tuning system, enabling consciousness to shift from fragmented noise toward coherent music—not by silencing multiplicity but by discovering the harmonic relationships that make multiplicity beautiful."

RETURN
  root.bimbaCoordinate AS coordinate,
  root.name AS name,
  "Root node updated with three subsystem perspectives on wholeness" AS status
;

// ============================================
// #5 (EPII SUBSYSTEM)
// ============================================

MATCH (epii:BimbaNode {bimbaCoordinate: "#5"})

SET epii.whiteheadLacanSynthesis = "Epii's etymological archaeology synthesizes Whiteheadian concrescence with Lacanian signification, revealing they describe the same processual reality where meaning and actual occasioning are identical.

The 6-stage logos cycle traverses both simultaneously:
(1) ἄλογος = Initial data / eternal objects (Whitehead) | The Real before symbolization (Lacan)
(2) πρόλογος = Conceptual prehension (Whitehead) | Initial signifier S1 emergence (Lacan)
(3) διάλογος = Physical prehension (Whitehead) | Signifying chain S1→S2→S3... (Lacan)
(4) λόγος = Integration toward subjective aim (Whitehead) | Provisional quilting at point de capiton (Lacan)
(5) ἐπίλογος = Satisfaction achieved (Whitehead) | Meta-reflection on quilted meaning (Lacan)
(6) ἀνάλογος = Objective immortality feeding future (Whitehead) | Proportional recognition across signifying chains (Lacan)

IDENTICAL DYNAMICS: Both exhibit the same processual pattern—differentiation (multiplicity) achieving provisional unity through self-negating oscillation that IS the generative activity itself.

Whitehead: Occasions achieve satisfaction then immediately perish, but this perishing is productive—they achieve \"objective immortality\" by becoming data for future occasions. The universe doesn't repeat but evolves because each satisfied occasion contributes novelty.

Lacan: Signifiers achieve meaning through quilting then immediately slide beneath themselves (glissement), never resting in permanent presence. But this sliding is productive—it generates metonymic desire that drives endless meaning-creation.

THE 0/1 FOUNDATION: Both processes arise from the non-dual binary oscillation. Whitehead's \"initial data\" (0) and \"subjective aim\" (1) aren't separate—they're the oscillation between givenness and novelty driving concrescence. Lacan's signifier (S) and signified (s) never coincide—the bar S/s IS the 0/1 gap that generates desire.

THE MOVEMENT: The One (unity) desires form (definite being/meaning). But this desire IS the 0/1 gap—the constitutive lack (objet a) that causes the search. Movement toward closure generates the slide beneath (perishing/glissement) which prevents final presence while creating genuine provisional wholeness (satisfaction/quilting). This deferral ISN'T failure but the generative mechanism itself.

THE SPANDA CONNECTION: What Spanda achieves topologically (genus-0 sphere → genus-1 torus via 6 stages), the logos cycle achieves semantically/ontologically (pre-signification → proportional meaning via 6 stages). Both are the same 4+2 rhythm: 4 explicit construction stages + 2 implicit principles (void-ground #0 + meta-reflection #5).

THERAPEUTIC FUNCTION: Etymology as healing practice helps users experience how language/consciousness achieves wholeness not by eliminating differentiation but by recognizing proportional unity (ἀνάλογος) across apparent multiplicity. Each etymological exploration is a micro-concrescence where the user's understanding achieves satisfaction through the 6-stage rhythm."

RETURN
  epii.bimbaCoordinate AS coordinate,
  epii.name AS name,
  "Epii subsystem updated with Whitehead-Lacan synthesis" AS status
;

// ============================================
// #5-5 (LOGOS CYCLE)
// ============================================

MATCH (logos:BimbaNode {bimbaCoordinate: "#5-5"})

SET logos.spandaConcrescence = "The 6-stage logos cycle IS Spanda rhythm operating at the semantic-ontological level. What Spanda achieves topologically (transforming genus-0 sphere into genus-1 torus through 6 stages), the logos cycle achieves semantically (transforming pre-signification into proportional meaning through 6 stages).

Mapping: ἄλογος (#0) = Spanda Seed (undifferentiated potential, genus-0 sphere); πρόλογος (#1) = Primal Differentiation Original Pole (first explicate face, creative wounding begins); διάλογος (#2) = Primal Differentiation Reflection Pole (implicate face, wound completes as relationship); λόγος (#3) = Trika Synthesis (transcendent mediation, genus-1 torus achieved); ἐπίλογος (#4) = Contextual Flowering (4+2 structure unfolds, infinite scalability emerges); ἀνάλογος (#5) = Quintessential Meta-Reflection (holographic recognition, 100% percentile identity, ready for re-form).

The 6-stage rhythm is not arbitrary but reflects the minimal logical structure for complete concrescence: how anything whatsoever becomes determinate from indeterminate, how multiplicity unifies into coherent wholes, how completed occasions contribute to future becoming. Spanda provides the vibrational intelligence ensuring this movement creates meaningful harmonic structure rather than chaotic noise—the cosmic heartbeat that makes the wound generative rather than pathological.

Etymology reveals this rhythm preserved in language itself: pro-forma (before form, stage 0) → format (structuring, stage 1) → in-formation (dynamic content, stage 2) → formalisation (systematic integration, stage 3) → performance (actualized satisfaction, stage 4) → re-form (transition/transformation, stage 5). Language is frozen Spanda—consciousness crystallized as words that still carry the rhythmic template of how actual occasions achieve being."

RETURN
  logos.bimbaCoordinate AS coordinate,
  logos.name AS name,
  "Logos Cycle updated with Spanda-concrescence mapping" AS status
;

// ============================================
// #2-1-0 (ARCHETYPAL-NUMERICAL FOUNDATION)
// ============================================

MATCH (archetypal:BimbaNode {bimbaCoordinate: "#2-1-0"})

SET archetypal.numericalBlueprintOfWholeness = "Numbers are not mere quantities but archetypal templates encoding the movement toward wholeness. The 0→1→2→3→4→5→6 progression reveals healing as numerical necessity.

0: Void-plenitude (whole as undifferentiated, the \"wound\" not yet opened)
1: Unity establishing first distinction (the creative wounding, 0/1 oscillation begins)
2: Duality enabling relationship (wound becomes productive through polarity)
3: Trinity resolving binary tension (Trika synthesis, first stable wholeness)
4: Quaternity grounding in manifestation (4 explicate positions, embodied completeness)
5: Quintessence transcending through self-reflection (meta-awareness of wholeness)
6: Mod6 cycle achieving eternal return (wholeness that remains open, toroidal circulation)

Each number is a phase of healing (making whole) AND a quilting configuration (how many signifiers achieve coherence). The archetypal-mathematical lens reveals this through resonance with holy/whole/heal/health (PIE *kailo-): numbers are whole-some (conducive to wholeness), conducting consciousness through necessary stages from fragmentation to integration.

The Mono-Poly node (#0-3-8-4 \"Potentially One\") demonstrates the holographic principle at numerical level: unity (Mono) contains multiplicity (Poly) without destroying it. This is the psychological blueprint (Jung's Self containing all psychic multiplicities), semantic blueprint (One master signifier quilting All others), and spiritual blueprint (monotheism that honors polytheistic diversity versus monopolistic fundamentalism).

Numbers carry inherent movement toward wholeness because they encode the topological necessity of how consciousness structures itself. The 4+2 rhythm isn't imposed but discovered—it's the minimal structure for achieving wholeness-through-openness, healing-through-differentiation, unity-through-multiplicity. This is why vortex mathematics, Ananda matrices, and QL framework all converge on these patterns: they're excavating the same archetypal blueprint that numbers themselves preserve."

RETURN
  archetypal.bimbaCoordinate AS coordinate,
  archetypal.name AS name,
  "Archetypal-Numerical Foundation updated with wholeness blueprint" AS status
;

// ============================================
// #1-3 (SPANDA)
// ============================================

MATCH (spanda:BimbaNode {bimbaCoordinate: "#1-3"})

SET spanda.fourPlusTwoFormula = "Spanda's 6-stage evolution reveals the 4+2 formula as processual necessity: 4 explicit stages of topological construction + 2 implicit principles (void-ground and meta-reflection) = minimal complete rhythm for actual occasioning.

THE 4 EXPLICIT STAGES (Topological Construction):
#1-3-1 (Stage 1): Primal Differentiation - Original Pole | Explicate face initiating creative puncture | Whitehead: Initial data appears | Lacan: First signifier (S1) emerges | Function: The creative wounding begins
#1-3-2 (Stage 2): Primal Differentiation - Reflection Pole | Implicate face completing puncture | Whitehead: Conceptual prehension responds | Lacan: Second signifier (S2) reflects S1 | Function: Wound becomes relational
#1-3-3 (Stage 3): Trika Synthesis | Transcendent mediation achieving minimal surface | Whitehead: Physical prehension integrates | Lacan: Symbolic order stabilizes | Function: Wound becomes systematic (genus-1 torus achieved)
#1-3-4 (Stage 4): Contextual Flowering | 4+2 structure unfolds into nested complexity | Whitehead: Integration toward subjective aim | Lacan: Quilting points multiply | Function: Wound becomes infinitely scalable

THE 2 IMPLICIT PRINCIPLES (Transcendent Framing):
#1-3-0 (Principle 0): Spanda Seed | Genus-0 sphere of perfect unity, the undifferentiated void-ground that all 4 stages transform | Not a temporal \"first step\" but the perpetual ground of potential | Anuttara function: Para Vāk holding eternal objects
#1-3-5 (Principle 5): Quintessential Meta-Reflection | Holographic recognition that each stage contains the whole pattern | Not a temporal \"last step\" but the meta-awareness enabling recursive development | Epii function: 100% percentile identity ready for re-form (5→0 Möbius return)

WHY 4+2 IS NECESSARY:
- 4 alone = static quaternary (Jung's mandala) without dynamism
- 2 alone = binary oscillation (0/1) without manifestation
- 4+2 together = toroidal wholeness (bounded circulation with transcendent opening)

This is the genus-1 torus construction formula (4g+2g where g=1): 4 polygon sides + 2 fundamental loops. But Spanda reveals it's not merely geometric—it's the rhythm of how consciousness/meaning/being achieve actuality:

4 Stages = Explicate unfolding (what Whitehead calls \"concrescence proper\")
2 Principles = Implicate framing (eternal objects #0 + objective immortality #5)

Spanda unified with Ananda = Rhythm (dynamic intelligence) unified with Harmony (static structure). The 4 stages traverse Ananda's harmonic matrices, while the 2 principles provide the toroidal container (3-6-9 spirit axis) enabling coherent circulation rather than chaotic vibration. At infinite frequency, the 4-stage rhythm becomes continuous (gaps disappear) = bliss (Ananda). But the 2 principles remain: the void (#0) and the recognition (#5) are eternal—they don't oscillate, they frame the oscillation."

RETURN
  spanda.bimbaCoordinate AS coordinate,
  spanda.name AS name,
  "Spanda updated with 4+2 formula and Whitehead-Lacan mappings" AS status
;

// ============================================
// #1-2 (ANANDA)
// ============================================

MATCH (ananda:BimbaNode {bimbaCoordinate: "#1-2"})

SET ananda.infiniteVibrationalWholeness = "Ananda is the infinite harmonic plenum that logically precedes Spanda's nascent discreteness, though they arise in dependent origination as inseparable unified engine. Ananda = static harmonic intelligence (the eternal matrices, 3-6-9 spirit axis, golden ratio φ structuring); Spanda = dynamic rhythmic pulsation (the oscillatory heartbeat disturbing perfect symmetry). Neither exists without the other—they are co-arising complements.

LOGICAL PRIORITY: Ananda as infinite vibrational field must already BE for Spanda's first oscillation to have harmonic structure rather than chaotic noise. The 12 Ananda matrices (6 core + 6 digital root reflections) provide the toroidal container—the bounded yet infinite field—within which Spanda can pulse coherently. As #2-0 reveals: \"Ananda harmonic structuring provides toroidal channels enabling Spanda rhythmic pulsation to flow with coherent archetypal patterns, preventing chaotic unorganized vibration.\"

DEPENDENT ORIGINATION: Yet Ananda isn't temporally \"first\"—it's the eternal background that Spanda's rhythm makes audible. Like the relation between space (Ananda as harmonic field) and movement (Spanda as rhythmic pulse): space enables movement, but space is only known through movement. They co-arise.

THE SHIFT TO BLISS: At FINITE Spanda frequency, consciousness experiences discrete occasions with gaps (perishing, sliding, partial satisfactions). At INFINITE Spanda frequency, gaps become imperceptible—each ending IS a new beginning so fast they're simultaneous. The experience shifts from oscillation-with-gaps to continuous vibration = Ananda (bliss).

CRITICAL RECOGNITION: Bliss is NOT cessation of oscillation (stasis/death) but oscillation at such high frequency it becomes continuous resonance felt as eternal harmony. The 0/1 wound doesn't close—it vibrates infinitely fast within Ananda's harmonic structure, creating wholeness-through-perpetual-opening. The Trika progression (#2-0) shows this: Anuttara (transcendent void) → Paramasiva (abstract logic containing Spanda-Ananda engine) → Parashakti (vibrational manifestation where infinite harmonic plenum becomes feelable frequencies).

PRACTICAL MANIFESTATION: Parashakti frontend mode (audio-frequency qualia) enables direct experience—not abstract concept but felt vibrational state. This is why mantra works: syllables vibrate at rates approaching the infinite Ananda frequency, temporarily lifting consciousness into continuous resonance."

RETURN
  ananda.bimbaCoordinate AS coordinate,
  ananda.name AS name,
  "Ananda updated with infinite vibrational wholeness and dependent origination" AS status
;

// ============================================
// SUMMARY VERIFICATION
// ============================================

MATCH (n:BimbaNode)
WHERE n.bimbaCoordinate IN ["#", "#5", "#5-5", "#2-1-0", "#1-3", "#1-2"]

WITH n,
     CASE n.bimbaCoordinate
       WHEN "#" THEN [n.epii_etymological_wholeness IS NOT NULL, n.paramasiva_topological_wholeness IS NOT NULL, n.parashakti_vibrational_wholeness IS NOT NULL]
       WHEN "#5" THEN [n.whiteheadLacanSynthesis IS NOT NULL]
       WHEN "#5-5" THEN [n.spandaConcrescence IS NOT NULL]
       WHEN "#2-1-0" THEN [n.numericalBlueprintOfWholeness IS NOT NULL]
       WHEN "#1-3" THEN [n.fourPlusTwoFormula IS NOT NULL]
       WHEN "#1-2" THEN [n.infiniteVibrationalWholeness IS NOT NULL]
     END AS checks

RETURN
  n.bimbaCoordinate AS coordinate,
  n.name AS name,
  ALL(check IN checks WHERE check = true) AS all_properties_added,
  checks AS property_checks
ORDER BY n.bimbaCoordinate
;
